# Supplied Accessories

The following are included with the camera:

- NP-W126S rechargeable battery
- Body cap (comes attached to camera)
- USB cable
- Headphone adapter
- Shoulder strap
- *Basic Manual*

> ⚠️ **Note:**
> - The battery is not charged at shipment. Charge the battery before use (📖 33).

> 💡 **Additional Information:**
> - If you purchased a lens kit, check that a lens is included.
> - Purchasers of the accessory kit should confirm that it includes a hand grip and thumb rest.
> - The supplied headphone adapter converts USB Type-C connectors to ø3.5 mm headphone jacks.
> - For information on compatible computer software, see “Software for Use with Your Camera” (📖 301).
